{
  "stem": "22047.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every so often, we'd fire off a few rounds across the river.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Never hit anybody, I don't think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they'd do the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans across the river would do the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was our initiation to combat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not much fighting, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was just a-- it was kind of-- kind of exciting, though.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, here, the enemy's right over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's across the river.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we're going to see him one of these days soon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Shortly thereafter, after about a week in this hacienda or this chateau, we went north to a-- a place called Schonenberg.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my particular job-- our company was assigned on what's called an outpost line.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And an outpost line is a line beyond the main line of resistance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And our job was to try to disorganize the enemy, to make him believe that we were the main line and commit his forces.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so we did that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I was-- my platoon-- I was a platoon leader then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My platoon was on the top of this hill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we could look down in this valley.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this-- we had taken over the foxholes from another unit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the night after we took over was the beginning in that particular sector of the Battle of the Bulge.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were sitting there on a line, not armed well enough.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We didn't have anti-tank weapons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and so we were fighting off tanks with machine guns and rifles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that's pretty hard to do with armored tanks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I recall looking down this valley.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was this tank with a bunch of German infantry following it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And one of my guys, it had to be 800 yards away from this tank and this infantry.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
